'''戈茲控股股份有限公司'''，簡稱'''戈茲控股股份'''、'''戈茲控股'''和'''KOC集團'''（'''{{lang-tr|Koç Holding A.Ş.}}'''），為[[土耳其|土耳其]]最大綜合企業公司，也是在2016年，唯一被[[财富世界500强|财富世界500强]]入榜。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://todayszaman.com/news-147240-koc-only-turkish-entry-on-fortune-global-500-list.html|title=Koç only Turkish entry on Fortune Global 500 list|work=TodaysZaman|accessdate=24 April 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127064628/http://www.todayszaman.com/news-147240-koc-only-turkish-entry-on-fortune-global-500-list.html|archivedate=27 January 2016}}</ref> 總部位於[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.koc.com.tr/en-us/Corporate/Headquarters/Pages/Nakkastepe.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-30 |archive-date=2011-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719053137/http://www.koc.com.tr/en-us/Corporate/Headquarters/Pages/Nakkastepe.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> 由著名富商{{tsl|en|Koç family|戈茲家族}}持有者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/forbes-2010-yilinin-milyarderler-listesini-acikladi/ekonomi/sondakika/11.03.2010/1209900/default.htm|title=Forbes, 2010 yÄ±lÄ±nÄ±n milyarderler listesini aÃ§Ä±kladÄ±|date=11 March 2010|publisher=|accessdate=24 April 2015|archive-date=2010-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100504144532/http://www.milliyet.com.tr/forbes-2010-yilinin-milyarderler-listesini-acikladi/ekonomi/sondakika/11.03.2010/1209900/default.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該公司由{{tsl|en|Vehbi Koç|維碧·戈茲}}於1963年創立，則在1926年扮演創業主要角色，成為以姓氏作為主要企業。<ref name="koc.com.tr">{{Cite web |url=http://www.koc.com.tr/en-us/Corporate/History/Pages/1926_until_Today.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-30 |archive-date=2011-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719054111/http://www.koc.com.tr/en-us/Corporate/History/Pages/1926_until_Today.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1984年，由維碧·戈茲兒子{{tsl|en|Rahmi Koç|納米·戈茲}}委任董事長一職。<ref name="koc.com.tr"/> 

2003年4月4日，納米·戈茲從董事長退任，改為名譽董事長銜頭，而大兒子{{tsl|en|Mustafa Vehbi Koç|穆斯它發·維碧·戈茲}}委任董事長一職<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R-ztAAAAMAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&dq=Rahmi+Ko%C3%A7+retired+and+handed+his+position+over+to+his+eldest+son+Mustafa+V.+Ko%C3%A7&q=Rahmi+Ko%C3%A7+retired+and+handed+his+position+over+to+his+eldest+son+Mustafa+V.+Ko%C3%A7&hl=en|title=The Economist|date=2003|publisher=Economist Newspaper Limited|language=en}}</ref>

2015年2月，朗維特·下吉洛魯（Levent Çakıroğlu）接替已離任吐吉·杜洛克（Turgay Durak）首席執行官一職。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/koc-holding-ceo-idUSL5N0VR25C20150217 |title=UPDATE 1-Turkish conglomerate Koc Holding names new CEO |website=reuters.com |date=2015-02-17 |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2017-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520093124/http://www.reuters.com/article/koc-holding-ceo-idUSL5N0VR25C20150217 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年第一季，穆斯它發·維碧·戈茲去世，改由{{tsl|en|Omer Koc|奧瑪·戈茲}}接任董事長一職。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ömer Koç becomes chairman of Turkey's largest conglomerate after death of brother Mustafa Koç|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/business/2016/02/22/omer-koc-becomes-chairman-of-turkeys-largest-conglomerate-after-death-of-brother-mustafa-koc|last=Wires|first=Daily Sabah with|date=2016-02-22|website=Daily Sabah|language=en|access-date=2020-05-14|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112082332/https://www.dailysabah.com/business/2016/02/22/omer-koc-becomes-chairman-of-turkeys-largest-conglomerate-after-death-of-brother-mustafa-koc|dead-url=no}}</ref>

